data.description: Explore luxury living in this spacious 3,258 sq. ft. home with 4 bedrooms, plus a 5th bonus room and 3 full bathrooms! Nestled in the heart of Winchester, California, this home boasts elegance, and comfort. When you enter this inviting residence, experience genuine hard wood flooring throughout the first level. The versatile downstairs bonus room can serve as a 5th bedroom! Alternatively, it offers the perfect space for a home office or playroom catering to various lifestyle needs. You can enjoy a quiet moment in the cozy lounge area, have dinner in the secondary formal dining room, gather around the open-concept kitchen accented with beautiful granite countertops, or choose to unwind in front of the fireplace of the spacious living area. Upstairs features a comfy loft, a large primary suite, three generously sized additional bedrooms, another bathroom with double sinks plus the benefit of a utility sink in the conveniently located laundry room. You will have the advantage of a 3-car tandem garage featuring an expansive extended driveway, offering increased storage space, flexibility for multiple vehicles, or the potential for a workshop or home gym. You can also gather with family and friends on the large covered back patio with ceiling fans, while enjoying the well-manicured landscaping. This home is the perfect blend of beauty and practicality! Just moments away from everything you would want, including wineries, shopping, dining, and easy freeway access! Come live the good life in Winchester!
